3|title=Allmusic: Clyde Stubblefield - The Original Funky Drummer Breakbeat Album|website=Allmusic |date=July 15, 2002|accessdate=November 20, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314033248/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-original-funky-drummer-breakbeat-album-mw0001483383|archivedate=March 14, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-original-am\">{{cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/the-original-mw0000329700|title=Allmusic: Clyde Stubblefield - The Original |website=Allmusic|date=November 25, 2003|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314095041/http://www.allmusic.com/album/the-original-mw0000329700|archivedate=March 14, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-original-albumnotes\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cdbaby.com/cd/stubblefieldc#cphContent_divAlbumNotes|title=CDBaby: The Original - Album Notes|publisher=cdbaby.com|date=2003|accessdate=April 2, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301214218/http://cdbaby.com/cd/stubblefieldc|archivedate=March 1, 2009|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-findgroove-am\">{{cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/find-the-groove-mw0000506127|title=Allmusic: Funkmasters - Find the Groove|publisher=Allmusic.com|date=2001|accessdate=March 22, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222174216/http://www.allmusic.com/album/find-the-groove-mw0000506127|archivedate=December 22, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cd-summathis-am\">{{cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/come-get-summa-this-mw0001262368|title=Allmusic: Funkmasters - Come Get Summa This|publisher=Allmusic.com|date=May 17, 2006|accessdate=March 22, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222175033/http://www.allmusic.com/album/come-get-summa-this-mw0001262368|archivedate=December 22, 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-instvideo-1999\">{{cite web|url=http://www.halleonard.com/product/viewproduct.do?itemid=320374&menuid=383&subsiteid=2&|title=C