 Kidney|author=Tom Alesia|newspaper=Wisconsin State Journal|date=July 28, 2009|accessdate=March 30, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121014145/http://host.madison.com/news/battling-the-blues-he-beat-cancer-but-now-r-b/article_cfad7c61-c97d-55ce-99ea-398b6d9945bb.html|archivedate=November 21, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-vicfirth-2010\">{{cite web|url=http://www.vicfirth.com/exchange/2010/09/09/where-old-school-meets-new-the-timeless-rhythm-of-clyde-stubblefield/|title=Where Old School Meets New \u2013 The Timeless Rhythm of Clyde Stubblefield|author=David Stanoch|publisher=vicfirth.com|date=September 9, 2010|accessdate=March 30, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009012413/http://www.vicfirth.com/exchange/2010/09/09/where-old-school-meets-new-the-timeless-rhythm-of-clyde-stubblefield/|archivedate=October 9, 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-moderndrummer-2007\">{{cite web|url=http://www.moderndrummer.com/site/2007/05/clyde-stubblefield/#_|title=Clyde Stubblefield|author=Kevin Kearns|work=Modern Drummer magazine|date=May 18, 2007|accessdate=March 22, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307152411/http://www.moderndrummer.com/site/2007/05/clyde-stubblefield#.VQ9JP-FM9F4|archivedate=March 7, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref> \n\n<ref name=\"cs-confreaks-2012\">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1qx5hm8HbA#t=15m14s|title=Madison Ruby 2012 - Clyde Stubblefield |publisher=youtube.com, Confreaks channel |date=July 30, 2015|accessdate=February 19, 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220005732/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1qx5hm8HbA|archivedate=February 20, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-imdb-2011\">{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1870860/|title=IMDb: Late Night with Jimmy Fallon \u2013 Episode 3.50|publisher=IMDb.com|date=March 29, 2011|accessdate=March 31, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401014951/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1870860