o-1999\">{{cite web|url=http://www.halleonard.com/product/viewproduct.do?itemid=320374&menuid=383&subsiteid=2&|title=Clyde Stubblefield & John \"Jab'o\" Starks \u2013 Soul of the Funky Drummers|publisher=Hal Leonard Corp.|isbn=9780634059919|date=1999|accessdate=March 24, 2015|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131223034835/http://www.halleonard.com/product/viewproduct.do?itemid=320374&menuid=383&subsiteid=2&|archivedate=December 23, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-tributeshow-2007\">{{cite web|url=http://www.cincygroove.com/?p=6395|title=Show Review \u2013 James Brown Tribute Show 12/22/07|author=Scott Preston|publisher=cincygroove.com|date=December 22, 2007|accessdate=March 22, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302045334/http://www.cincygroove.com/?p=6395|archivedate=March 2, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-ffya-2008\">{{cite web|url=http://www.discogs.com/Fred-Wesley-featuring-Jabo-Starks-Clyde-Stubblefield-with-Bootsy-Collins-Funk-For-Your-Ass-A-Tribute/release/1884224|title=Funk For Your Ass (A Tribute To The Godfather Of Soul) |publisher=Discogs.com|date=May 28, 2008|accessdate=March 22, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210005814/http://www.discogs.com/Fred-Wesley-featuring-Jabo-Starks-Clyde-Stubblefield-with-Bootsy-Collins-Funk-For-Your-Ass-A-Tribute/release/1884224|archivedate=February 10, 2010|url-status=live}}(Fred Wesley featuring Jab'o Starks & Clyde Stubblefield with Bootsy Collins)</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-toon-2008\">{{cite web|url=http://www.toontrack.com/news.asp?id=138|title=Toontrack Music announces the release of the Funkmasters EZX|publisher=Toontrack|date=November 6, 2008|accessdate=March 24, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201000339/http://www.toontrack.com/news.asp?id=138|archivedate=February 1, 2009|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"cs-madison-jul2009\">{{cite news|url=http://host.madison.com/news/battling-the-blues-he-beat-cancer-but-now-r-b/article_cfad7c61-c97d-